data.description: Welcome to this spacious and inviting 2-story home! This well-designed residence features a main bedroom on the ground floor, providing convenience and privacy. With a total of 4 bedrooms and 2.5 baths.  The open floor plan creates a seamless flow throughout the main living spaces, including a generously sized living area perfect for gatherings and relaxation. Adjacent to this, you'll find a separate formal dining area, ideal for hosting dinner parties and special occasions.  Upstairs, a versatile media room awaits, offering endless possibilities for entertainment, a home office, or a playroom. The remaining bedrooms provide ample space and comfort for the entire family.  Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this house your home. Schedule a viewing today and experience the convenience and luxury of living in this beautiful property
